\pard\plain \fi720\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 So much technology has been twisted to evil means that Heka bids me to ask for an oath from anyone who would use this knowledge to acquire }{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 heka}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  (magic power or authority with the }{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 ka}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ).}
